{"_path":"/maps/_ai/training/post-training","_dir":"training","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Post-training","description":"Post-training optimization and model alignment","original_path":"_ai/post-training.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"后训练-post-training"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"后训练 (Post-Training)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"dpo直接偏好优化的对齐革命"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DPO：直接偏好优化的对齐革命"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DPO（Direct Preference Optimization）将 RLHF 的两阶段流程（训练 Reward Model + PPO 优化）压缩为单阶段。它直接在偏好数据上优化策略，数学上等价于带 KL 约束的 RL，但实现更简单、训练更稳定。无需强化学习，只需监督学习即可完成对齐，大大降低了后训练门槛。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.18290","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DPO 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://cameronrwolfe.substack.com/p/direct-preference-optimization","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DPO 详解 - Deep Learning Focus"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.philschmid.de/rl-with-llms-in-2025-dpo","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 DPO 对齐指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"grpodeepseek-r1-的推理突破关键"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GRPO：DeepSeek-R1 的推理突破关键"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GRPO（Group Relative Policy Optimization）是 DeepSeek-R1 实现 reasoning 能力突破的核心技术。与传统 PPO 需要独立的 Critic 模型不同，GRPO 通过组内采样估计 baseline——对同一问题生成多组回答，以组内得分的相对排名作为优势估计，显存开销降低 50%，让超长思维链（Chain-of-Thought）的训练成为可能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2501.12948","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSeek-R1 技术报告"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://medium.com/@sahin.samia/the-math-behind-deepseek-a-deep-dive-into-group-relative-policy-optimization-grpo-8a75007491ba","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GRPO 数学原理"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://unsloth.ai/blog/r1-reasoning","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unsloth GRPO 本地训练"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"orposft-与对齐的合并"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ORPO：SFT 与对齐的合并"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ORPO（Odds Ratio Preference Optimization）将传统两阶段流程（先 SFT 再 DPO）合并为单阶段。它用一个损失函数同时优化指令跟随和偏好对齐，训练效率提升一倍，且无需参考模型。这是目前最高效的后训练方法之一。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2403.07691","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ORPO 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/en/orpo_trainer","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hugging Face ORPO Trainer"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.analyticsvidhya.com/blog/2024/05/finetuning-llama-3-with-odds-ratio-preference-optimization/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Llama 3 ORPO 微调"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"simpo更简单直接的偏好优化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SimPO：更简单直接的偏好优化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SimPO 进一步简化 DPO，移除参考模型，直接优化响应间的胜率。它引入\"长度归一化\"，避免模型生成冗长但空洞的回复，是对 DPO 的实用改进。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/en/index","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SimPO 介绍"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"trl后训练的一站式解决方案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRL：后训练的一站式解决方案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRL（Transformer Reinforcement Learning）是 Hugging Face 生态中的后训练全栈库，集成 SFT、DPO、PPO、GRPO、Reward Modeling 等方法。它与 transformers、peft、datasets 无缝协作，是入门后训练的首选工具。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/huggingface/trl","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRL GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/en/index","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRL 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"后训练最佳实践数据质量-数量"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"后训练最佳实践：数据质量 > 数量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"偏好对的质量远胜于数量——1000 条精心标注的偏好对 > 10000 条噪声数据。推荐流程：冷启动（高质量 SFT 建立基础指令跟随能力）→ 多轮对齐（SFT → DPO → RL，逐步逼近目标分布）→ 能力保持（定期在基础能力测试集上评估，防止对齐税）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.53ai.com/news/finetuning/2026010417029.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 微调全指南"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"dpo直接偏好优化的对齐革命","depth":2,"text":"DPO：直接偏好优化的对齐革命"},{"id":"grpodeepseek-r1-的推理突破关键","depth":2,"text":"GRPO：DeepSeek-R1 的推理突破关键"},{"id":"orposft-与对齐的合并","depth":2,"text":"ORPO：SFT 与对齐的合并"},{"id":"simpo更简单直接的偏好优化","depth":2,"text":"SimPO：更简单直接的偏好优化"},{"id":"trl后训练的一站式解决方案","depth":2,"text":"TRL：后训练的一站式解决方案"},{"id":"后训练最佳实践数据质量-数量","depth":2,"text":"后训练最佳实践：数据质量 > 数量"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:training:post-training.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/training/post-training.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/training/post-training","_extension":"md"}